title: 无线速率是多少？
answer:
802.11b模式（支持1 Mbit/s、 2 Mbit/s、 5.5 Mbit/s、11 Mbit/s）；
802.11g模式（支持1 Mbit/s、 2 Mbit/s、 5.5 Mbit/s、6 Mbit/s、11 Mbit/s,12 Mbit/s、 18 Mbit/s、24 Mbit/s、36 Mbit/s、48 Mbit/s、 54 Mbit/s）；
802.11n模式（支持6.5 Mbit/s, 13.0 Mbit/s, 13.5 Mbit/s, 19.5 Mbit/s, 26.0 Mbit/s, 27.0 Mbit/s, 39.0 Mbit/s, 40.5 Mbit/s, 52.0 Mbit/s, 54.0 Mbit/s, 58.5Mbit/s, 65.0 Mbit/s, 78.0 Mbit/s, 81.0 Mbit/s, 104.0 Mbit/s, 108.0 Mbit/s, 117.0 Mbit/s, 121.5 Mbit/s, 130.0 Mbit/s, 135.0 Mbit/s, 162.0 Mbit/s, 216.0 Mbit/s, 243.0 Mbit/s, 270.0 Mbit/s, and 300.0 Mbit/s）。
